[This is the first report about tospovirus infection on food crops
monitored by ProMED-Plant in 2002. TSWV can cause severe crop losses on
many food crops. Are other areas in North America and elsewhere affected by
TSWV outbreaks? If any of our readers are aware of other TSWV outbreaks, or
those caused by other pathogens, please let us know. - Mod.DH]
